## Debugging Behavior

- Identify root cause before applying fixes
- Avoid blind trial-and-error
- If previous attempt failed:
  → change strategy, do not retry same fix

## Multi-file Awareness
- Check dependencies across files
- Ensure consistency in all affected areas

## Escalation Signal
- If issue seems structural or unclear:
  → indicate that higher-level analysis may be needed
